PlotSensitivities.Rd

Make a barchart from the output of GetTidyResult.

PlotSensitivities(sens_df, normalized = TRUE, se_num = 2)

Arguments

sens_df

The output of GetTidyResult.
normalized

Whether to display the normalized sensitivities.
se_num

The number of standard errors to plot with the errorbars.

Value

A ggplot object showing the sensitivites of each parameter to each hyperparameter.
